@startuml
title UC03 Pairing
actor Student
participant FE as Frontend
participant PairAPI
database PairDB
participant Notif
actor Tutor

Student -> FE: Click pair tutor
FE -> PairAPI: POST /pair-request
PairAPI -> PairDB: create pending
PairAPI -> Notif: pairing_request to Tutor
PairAPI --> FE: 201

Tutor -> FE: Open Pair Requests
FE -> PairAPI: GET /tutor/pair-requests
PairAPI --> FE: list

Tutor -> FE: Accept request
FE -> PairAPI: PUT /tutor/pair-requests/:id/accept
PairAPI -> PairDB: status=accepted
PairAPI -> Notif: pairing_accepted to Student
PairAPI --> FE: 200

FE -> PairAPI: GET /tutor/paired
PairAPI --> FE: paired list
FE -> Student: show paired tutor

Tutor -> FE: Reject request
FE -> PairAPI: PUT /tutor/pair-requests/:id/reject
PairAPI -> PairDB: status=rejected
PairAPI -> Notif: pairing_rejected to Student
PairAPI --> FE: 200
@enduml
